@startuml
!theme plain
title Consistency Problem: Update DB First, then Cache

actor "Request A" as A
actor "Request B" as B
entity "Cache" as Cache
database "Database" as DB

A -> DB : Update DB to 1
B -> DB : Update DB to 2
B -> Cache : Update cache to 2
A -> Cache : Update cache to 1

note over A, Cache #LightPink
**Result: DB = 2, Cache = 1 -> Data inconsistency**
end note

@enduml